sentences: Kim Loraine Appleby (born 28 August 1961) is an English singer, songwriter, and actress.
Kim released her first solo album Kim Appleby, in November 1990.
section: == Solo music career ==

sentences: One of these songs, "Don't Worry", was selected as the first single, and reached number two in the British charts in November 1990, as well as being a huge hit in Europe.
